  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.label>沃芬族军工巨型企业</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.label>
  <!-- EN: MegaCorp, officially known as the Wolfein MegaCorp, handles all aspects of a Wolfein's life, from birth to death. As the name suggests, its primary focus is on developing the military-industrial sector to satisfy the board's endless expansion demands. -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.description>沃芬军工巨型企业，包揽了沃芬族从出生到死亡的所有业务。正如其名，该企业的主要业务方向是发展军工产业，以满足董事会无止境的扩张需求。</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.description>
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.fixedName>沃芬军工巨企</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.fixedName>
  <!-- EN: Regional Supervisor -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.leaderTitle>区域主管</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.leaderTitle>
